37:56.578 --> 38:02.541
♪

38:02.671 --> 38:08.329
♪

38:08.460 --> 38:10.592
How did you find me?

38:10.723 --> 38:12.507
I figured it was you
as soon as the Collectors

38:12.638 --> 38:15.554
started showing up
to the island without fingers.

38:20.646 --> 38:24.345
No one else could be
that precise.

38:24.476 --> 38:26.216
Then when I heard
a transport got hit

38:26.347 --> 38:29.481
with a kid who needed surgery
on board,

38:29.611 --> 38:31.700
I knew you'd come here.

38:31.831 --> 38:34.268
June, what the hell
is going on?

38:34.399 --> 38:37.750
I assume Blue Jay told you
what this place used to be.

38:37.880 --> 38:39.795
How much promise it had.

38:39.926 --> 38:41.449
Promise?

38:41.580 --> 38:43.146
That what you call
murdering people?

38:43.277 --> 38:46.715
We never killed anyone.

38:46.846 --> 38:48.587
No.

38:48.717 --> 38:51.285
This place was about
saving lives.

38:51.416 --> 38:52.852
Protecting the future
of PADRE.

38:52.982 --> 38:54.680
You're full of shit.

38:54.810 --> 38:56.856
You're the one who lied to PADRE
about what you were doing today.

38:56.986 --> 39:00.512
I brought Finch here to keep him
safe from assholes like you.

39:00.642 --> 39:03.602
No one wants these children safe
more than PADRE.

39:03.732 --> 39:06.256
That is why this place
is so important.

39:06.387 --> 39:07.780
What we were doing here
could have protected

39:07.910 --> 39:11.044
these children
from Carrion.

39:11.174 --> 39:13.046
Can you imagine?

39:13.176 --> 39:15.178
But Blue Jay ran off before
she could perfect the cure.

39:15.309 --> 39:16.963
Cure?

39:17.093 --> 39:18.573
Everyone
we tried it on died.

39:18.704 --> 39:20.967
That was then.

39:21.097 --> 39:24.100
But I have faith you'll
get it right this time.

39:24.231 --> 39:26.189
This time?

39:26.320 --> 39:28.278
PADRE's got
something planned,

39:28.409 --> 39:31.978
something big,
expansive.

39:32.108 --> 39:35.285
He wants these children to be
as safe as they can be.

39:37.810 --> 39:39.028
You need to pick up
where you left off.

39:39.159 --> 39:41.683
I w-won't do that.

39:41.814 --> 39:42.902
You will.

39:43.032 --> 39:44.860
You just need
a little motivation.

39:51.040 --> 39:53.347
[Growling]

39:53.478 --> 39:59.005
♪

39:59.135 --> 40:04.880
♪

40:05.011 --> 40:06.926
-Hey.
-Hey.

40:07.056 --> 40:08.884
Hey! Hey!

40:09.015 --> 40:11.278
Dwight: No, no, no,
no, no, no, no!

40:11.409 --> 40:13.106
[Crying]

40:13.236 --> 40:15.325
Please don't.Stop, please! Stop it!

40:15.456 --> 40:16.675
Finch, wake up! Finch!No, no. Please stop.

